么想怎么做？我的想法是反人类吗？ 相关问题：如果一个人的死能拯救成千上万的人，那该不该剥夺他的生命？ - 道德"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ild+cuei6uPcmEAMaBzc3MDk4MjgggKfhswUwtgE4zjdAMHIIMzg3NTYyNzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-6142d3a86157970d670906628843bc76_720w.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"49_1626613905.3749554","card_id":"Q_319279638","target":{"id":319279638,"title":"你玩过哪些密室让你感觉想让全世界都知道「这才是密室逃脱啊」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/319279638","type":"question","created":1554715602,"answer_count":90,"follower_count":3566,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[52591,111976,169902],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"都坐标一下城市"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ild+cuei6uPcmEAMaCDMzMjI3MTkwINKnrOUFMAE47htAMXIJMzE5Mjc5NjM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-8a835f54e017537249e348a8b4469f8f_b.jpg"}]}],"description":{"time":"2021-07-18 21:11:45"}}